<HEADLINE>
NFL SUITOR BROAD WAIVES EXCLUSIVITY
</HEADLINE>
 (For use by NYTimes News Service clients) 
(EDITORS: Today in last graf refers to Tuesday.)  
 
  
BY STEVE DILBECK 
c.1999 Los Angeles Daily News  
<TEXT>
<P>
   ATLANTA _ If Michael Ovitz was going for the pizazz and Eli
