<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-05-25 10:46 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A0101 &Cx1f; tdt-z
u a &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-GENES-HEART-BOS &LR;      05-25 0513
