<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-05-25 11:04 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A6271 &Cx1f; tab-z
r a &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-CNS-STADIUMS-CASH &LR;      05-25 1747
