worldwide, some estimates range as high as 20 million.
 &HT;    ``Nobody had ever seen anything as cool as Doom,'' Romero says.
``The music, the sound effects, how scary it was, the attitude,
weapons balance, everything was perfect about that game.''
 &HT;    But even as Doom and its successor, Quake, became wildly
successful, a fundamental disagreement erupted between their
