<P>
   REACHING-OUT _ ATLANTA _ Columbine has reached out to Rockdale
County with flowers and other tokens of goodwill now that the two
are linked by school shootings. The last Heritage High School
shooting victim, Stephanie Laster, came home from the hospital
Tuesday. (Stafford, Atlanta Journal-Constitution)
</P>
