<SLUG> BC-ENVIRONMENT-0526-COX </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
&HT;   
</HEADLINE>
 &HT;    POLLUTION IN MINORITY COMMUNITIES TARGETED
 &HT;    Moving in (w) Washington and (a) general news categories
 &HT;    By Raven Hill
 &HT;    c. 1999 Cox News Service
