<SLUG> BC-SFCHRON-SF </SLUG>
 CHRON  
Editors Note: The San Francisco Chronicle's weekly food package
will move Wednesday, May 25.
<TEXT>
<P>
</P>
</TEXT>
</BODY>
<TRAILER>
NYT-05-25-99 2001EDT &QL; 
</TRAILER>
