   (NYT14) NEW YORK -- May 25, 1999 -- CHEF-GEOMANCY, 5-25 -- Eric
Ripert, one of at least a dozen chefs, including Daniel Boulud,
Francois Payard and Jean-Louis Palladin, who look to a 42-year-old
