Republican chairman, Rep. Christoper Cox, left, and four other
Representatives, Bobby Scott, Lucille Roybal-Allard, Norm Dicks,
the ranking Democrat on the committee, and Doug Bereuter. (Stephen
Crowley/New York Times Photo)
</P>
