<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-05-25 21:55 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A1018 &Cx1f; taf-z
u f &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-MAFIA-AD-COLUMN-NYT &LR;      05-25 0994
