</HEADER>
<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-NY-LOUIMA-TEXT-NYT </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
BRUTAL ACTS AND RAGE RECOUNTED 
</HEADLINE>
  (With NY-LOUIMA-TRIAL and related stories) 
(mk) 
 c.1999 N.Y. Times News Service   
<TEXT>
<P>
   Following are excerpts from the transcript of the guilty plea
entered by Justin Volpe in U.S. District Court in Brooklyn, N.Y.,
Tuesday before Judge Eugene Nickerson. In making the plea, Volpe
was required to disclose details of his participation in the crime.
</P>
<P>
   The Attack and Prelude
</P>
<P>
   Volpe: At the Club Rendezvous I got into a fight with Abner
Louima. During this altercation I was struck by an individual and
knocked to the ground. When I regained my composure, I saw this
individual, whom I believed to be Abner Louima, running towards the
corner of Farragut and Flatbush Avenue. I now know that this
individual was not Abner Louima. I gave chase but I never seen him
again. The next time I saw Louima was at the location of Glenwood
and Bedford Avenue, where in the presence of other officers I
struck Louima once while we proceeded in the patrol car.
</P>
<P>
   While in the bathroom _ while in the bathroom at the precinct,
in the presence of another officer, I sodomized Louima by placing a
stick in his rectum. I then threatened to kill him if he told
anybody.
</P>
<P>
   For Patrick Antoine, while I was chasing Louima in the area of
Glenwood and Flatbush, a man who I later learned to be Patrick
Antoine was chasing me and I yelled at him, ``Why are you chasing
me?'' I pushed him and was knocked to the ground by another
officer, Officer Schofield. I then continued running after the man
who I thought was Abner Louima. I then caused the complaint to be
issued from the D.A.'s office against Patrick Antoine charging him
with assault on me.
</P>
<P>
   2nd Officer
</P>
<P>
   Volpe: While I was in the bathroom, there was another police
officer in the bathroom with me. That police officer saw what was
going on, did nothing to stop it. It was understood from the
circumstances that that police officer would do nothing to stop me
or report it to anyone.
</P>
<P>
   Intent to Humiliate
</P>
<P>
   Judge Nickerson: Going back to the assault in the bathroom and
when you put the stick out towards his face, having shoved it into
his rectum, was a part of your effort to humiliate him?
</P>
<P>
   Volpe: I was in shock at the time, your Honor.
</P>
<P>
   Nickerson: You did intend to humiliate him, did you?
</P>
<P>
   Volpe: I intended to show it to him because _ I couldn't believe
what happened. Yes, if that humiliating him, I'm sure it did.
</P>
<P>
   Nickerson: Well, you intended to humiliate him, did you? You
thought you were mad at him?
</P>
<P>
   Volpe: I was mad at the time, yes.
</P>
<P>
   Nickerson: You intended to humiliate him?
</P>
<P>
   Volpe: Yes.
</P>
</TEXT>
</BODY>
